                            <comment id="13149563" author="dejanb" created="Mon, 14 Nov 2011 10:58:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;BooleanEditor is now used for createConnector property, which will enable it to be substituted even when schema validation is used. For older versions, you can explicitly turn off schema validation by using config &quot;xbean:activemq.xml?validate=false&quot;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
